Body (HTML): About the JYM Multivitamin: Supported Goals: Heart Health - Immune Function - Joint Health - Mind - Energy - Recovery. What It Is: Vita JYM is a high-potency multivitamin and mineral supplement designed specifically for athletes and active individuals to truly provide adequate amounts of the vitamins and minerals that are essential to hard-training individuals due to their higher requirements of these micronutrients coupled with a greater loss of these micronutrients from the body during exercise. The truth is that most people cannot take a one-a-day multi if they expect to maximize the uptake and utilization of those vitamins and minerals. So those three minerals have been removed from Vita JYM and placed in other products. ZMA JYM provides the zinc and magnesium the body needs at the right time. And Pro JYM and Mass JYM provide 400 mg and 500 mg of naturally occurring calcium from milk, respectively. The best form of calcium you can get without interfering with your uptake. Taken as directed, these micronutrients don't interfere with one another or other micronutrients, and the uptake and utilization of all vitamins and minerals are maximized, as will be the results. In addition, Vita JYM includes 5 mg of Bioperine, which has been shown to enhance the body's uptake of numerous vitamins and minerals. Using JYM supplements in this manner, not only helps to get optimal levels of each micronutrient but also helps to prevent supplying too much of any given micronutrient. For example, a multivitamin may provide 30 mg of zinc.. Vita JYM is a high-potency multivitamin and mineral supplement designed specifically for athletes and active individuals to provide optimal amounts of the vitamins and minerals essential to maximizing performance and recovery. Vita JYM contains 25 of the most critical micronutrients for hard-training athletes, including Vitamins A, B-complex, C, E and K, and iron, selenium, and chromium among others.
